like they would be for a festival!

00:21:44.160 --> 00:21:47.730
With you, Dia-chan, I can go anywhere.

00:21:53.930 --> 00:21:54.730
Yeah!

00:22:02.390 --> 00:22:09.220
Kitasan! Kitasan!

00:22:09.830 --> 00:22:13.720
That's right. If the two of
us are together... I know it!

00:22:13.720 --> 00:22:14.920
Yeah!

